  "detailed_description": "After working all your life you finally managed to build a device that allows you to travel between parallel worlds. Traveling you will discover a terrible threat, will you be able to return home?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/eb27ed23193adb2a03ddb10e86fb1a64.avif?t=1755370779\" width=628 height=353 /></span><br><br>It's a first-person linear narrative adventure with some more action sections.<br>The gameplay consists of interacting with the environment and doing things to advance the story, whit some fps, platforming, horror and stealth sections. Are you ready to go on your journey?<br><br><br>explore and survive..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/695a62636730004927ef9d1f9bf4d23a.poster.avif?t=1755370779\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/695a62636730004927ef9d1f9bf4d23a.webm?t=1755370779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/695a62636730004927ef9d1f9bf4d23a.mp4?t=1755370779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>solve puzzles..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/f1e31d3b23157c37577a8bcfec375ae3.poster.avif?t=1755370779\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/f1e31d3b23157c37577a8bcfec375ae3.webm?t=1755370779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/f1e31d3b23157c37577a8bcfec375ae3.mp4?t=1755370779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>defeat the enemies..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/00a1765d393d60acd803a7e4385ccfe1.poster.avif?t=1755370779\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/00a1765d393d60acd803a7e4385ccfe1.webm?t=1755370779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/00a1765d393d60acd803a7e4385ccfe1.mp4?t=1755370779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Developed by one person with unreal engine 5 , it is possible to reduce the graphic quality to make it work on older hardware, however a modern gpu is recommended.",
