o/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>defeat the enemies..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/00a1765d393d60acd803a7e4385ccfe1.poster.avif?t=1755370779\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/00a1765d393d60acd803a7e4385ccfe1.webm?t=1755370779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321690/extras/00a1765d393d60acd803a7e4385ccfe1.mp4?t=1755370779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Developed by one person with unreal engine 5 , it is possible to reduce the graphic quality to make it work on older hardware, however a modern gpu is recommended.",
